title: I am moving from a Pixel 3 to a Pixel 4 ... it copied over most things ... but not my wallpaper
content: I'm trying to copy over my wallpaper from my Pixel 3 to a Pixel 4. I transferred files over phone-to-phone using a cable ... but my wallpaper didn't come over and I can't find it (it's a picture I had taken years ago) and I cannot find it in any file manager.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4
